>26:33</a>. <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/curse-curses?lang=spa\"><small>GEE</small> Maldecir, maldiciones</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"7\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note7a\" data-full-marker=\"7a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124201204\" id=\"note7a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/12.23?lang=spa#p23\">1 Ne. 12:23</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"8\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note8a\" data-full-marker=\"8a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124201207\" id=\"note8a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/marriage-marry?lang=spa\"><small>GEE</small> Matrimonio — El matrimonio entre personas de distintas religiones</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note8b\" data-full-marker=\"8b\">\n<p data-aid=\"124201209\" id=\"note8b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/10.11-18?lang=spa#p11\">Mos. 10:11–18</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/9.16?lang=spa#p16\">Alma 9:16</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"11\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note11a\" data-full-marker=\"11a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124201211\" id=\"note11a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/17.9-11?lang=spa#p9\">Alma 17:9–11</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"12\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note12a\" data-full-marker=\"12a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124201213\" id=\"note12a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/1.6?lang=spa#p6\">Mos. 1:6</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/ether/4.6-11?lang=spa#p6\">Éter 4:6–11</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"13\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note13a\" data-full-marker=\"13a\">\n<p data-a